# Ybx1 rescue primers for RNA

This document contains information about constructs that will be used for profiling RNA levels of the rescue constructs for YB-1 engineered in the piggyBac vectors.

## Individual constructs

These are the original sequences that were synthesized and inserted into the cells. These will be the basis for our primer design. For primer design, I am using the [PrimerBlast](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/tools/primer-blast/index.cgi) tool from NCBI.
